OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry Wednesday but rain spreading east
OL,7,Flater. A few early showers on
OL,8,FThursday, otherwise dry, bright and
OL,9,Fbreezy. Mostly dry in east on Friday,
OL,10,Fsome cloud and rain west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
